FBIS4-59214 "drnes091_l_94011" FBIS-NES-94-091 Daily Report 7 May 1994 ISRAEL Golan Businessmen Prepare for Syrian Sovereignty Golan Businessmen Prepare for Syrian Sovereignty TA0705105394 Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el in Hebrew 0800 GMT 7 May 94 TA0705105394 Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el Hebrew BFN [Text] Some of the Golan Heights entrepreneurs and investors are preparing to continue running their businesses under Syrian sovereignty. Moreover, they say they have learned that this issue was anchored in the proposals Israel has submitted to Syria. Investments amounting to hundreds of millions of shekels continue to be made in the Golan Heights industry, agriculture, and infrastructure. A major part of the investments come from government funds.
